name: Cube Force Advanced
description:
Cube Force Advanced is a one-button puzzle platformer made by MDS students. You play a cube restricted to jumping up and down. Use moving platforms to your advantage to reach the objective!

Artists:

  • Greg Jonas
  • Sakthivel (Zak) Radhakrishna
  • Luke McCarty

Programmers:

  • Jarlin Barnard
  • Liam Haliday
